WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.880 --> 00:00:05.400
Spring is here!
Today, we'll show you the exciting trends

00:00:05.400 --> 00:00:10.660
in shapes and styles, and fresh, new colors
for your jewelry wardrobe... all in full bloom right now.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:21.000
A good place to start styling your spring wardrobe

00:00:21.269 --> 00:00:25.609
is with texture.
It brings interest and movement to your look

00:00:25.609 --> 00:00:30.509
-- as does the hottest trend in jewelry,
Diamonds in Rhythm.

00:00:30.509 --> 00:00:35.510
This collection of necklaces and earrings
features a shimmering center diamond that's

00:00:35.510 --> 00:00:40.280
always in motion.
Count on diamonds, paired with floral prints,

00:00:40.280 --> 00:00:46.460
to be the go-to choice this spring and summer.
Engagement rings in cuts like pear and emerald

00:00:46.460 --> 00:00:50.390
are sure to catch your eye.
Look for these center stones on brides-to-be

00:00:50.390 --> 00:00:57.390
at engagement parties and bridal showers.
"The" color of spring 2014 is Radiant Orchid.

00:00:57.390 --> 00:01:03.450
Pair it with jewelry in strong complementary
colors...like yellow diamonds... or bold citrine.

00:01:03.450 --> 00:01:07.000
Pairing jewel tones is 
what making a statement is all about.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:12.590
Jewelry in blue and its many shades and variations
are back in style this year.

00:01:12.590 --> 00:01:16.960
Opt for these blue and white diamond studs
to complement an intricate pattern like this

00:01:16.960 --> 00:01:21.369
blue paisley top.
Color diamonds really are springing up everywhere

00:01:21.369 --> 00:01:28.369
this season, in a rainbow of colors, like
blue, yellow...and black and blue.

00:01:28.829 --> 00:01:32.020
With jewelry as in fashion, it's all about
the details.

00:01:32.020 --> 00:01:36.420
The zipper on this Dazzling Blue dress adds
a casual flare.

00:01:36.420 --> 00:01:42.310
Play up the look with a diamond infinity bracelet
-- a new twist that's trending now.

00:01:42.310 --> 00:01:46.439
Complementary colors create a statement.
Give extra pop to that sizzling orange with

00:01:46.439 --> 00:01:50.909
this Blue topaz collection.
For an elegant spring evening look, combine

00:01:50.909 --> 00:01:57.249
vivid green with diamond-accented tanzanite.
Casual has a style all its own.

00:01:57.249 --> 00:02:04.020
Make your look 'now' by bringing tanzanite
together with this pale, fresh green cardigan.

00:02:04.020 --> 00:02:09.099
Rose gold continues to trend this spring!
Complement feminine lace with this equally

00:02:09.099 --> 00:02:13.970
feminine metal color.
For a look that's always in style, pair

00:02:13.970 --> 00:02:20.200
Le Vian strawberry gold and rich raspberry
rhodolite with neutral shades.

00:02:20.200 --> 00:02:24.780
Wear these trends with confidence and you
are guaranteed to look fabulous this spring!

